Run at start
cat /sys/class/net/eno1/statistics/tx_bytes
cat /sys/class/net/eno1/statistics/rx_bytes

Run at end
cat /sys/class/net/eno1/statistics/tx_bytes
cat /sys/class/net/eno1/statistics/rx_bytes

Calc difference between tx and rx between start and finish. Measures total amount of data that goes over the ethernet port. 